## 1. Introduction
Primordial Elemental Tic-Tac-Toe is an enhanced version of Tic-Tac-Toe played on a default 9×9 grid. Players compete to align their elemental symbols and accumulate points. Alignments and bonuses trigger additional effects, creating deep and dynamic gameplay.

## 2. Architecture & Technologies
- **Framework:** React (TypeScript)
- **Main Language:** TypeScript (front-end logic, game mechanics)
- **Server:** Node.js with Express and Socket.IO
